node.text:
Another interesting solution to make spaces more functional and convenient while ensuring that no space is wasted. The Easy Step makes it easier for short people or kids to open the top drawers. At the same time, under the step there is a fully functional box storage. It is designed by Blum | Video by @molina.design.krd 

.
.
.
.
.
.

node.text:
They were commissioned by Olympia Trust Company to create their new boardroom table. 
They selected an irregular 16’ slab of claro walnut that normally would be unusable for a table this size. 
In order to make the piece functional we cast it in 270L of our Deep Resin. We tinted the resin with black liquid dye to provide a nice contrast with the walnut. 
In order to get the piece up 22 floors, the built it in two pieces and took it up through the elevator!
.
.
.
.
.

node.text:
Would you swim? 
Check out @hobopeeba's perspective of the most jaw-dropping pool in the world. If you're looking for the finest rooftop spaces in London, feast your eyes on this world-famous Sky Pool that seems to float in the air. 🏴󠁧󠁢󠁥󠁮󠁧󠁿

Located in the Nine Elms district, this exclusive 25-meter-long pool connects two blocks of apartments. Built by structural engineers Eckersley O'Callaghan and designed by HAL Architects, it's known as the world's first floating transparent 'sky pool'. 💦

Did you know this pool existed in London and would you take a dip in it? 😄

📽 @hobopeeba
📍 London, England
🎶 Måneskin - Beggin'

The Rumah Beton House is a contemporary home situated in a high-density area, which means that the security and privacy of the residents were the main requirement. The result was an enclosed facade of wooden lattice creating an aesthetically beautiful look where the residents could still see the outside, but people outside could not see the inside. The house is designed by Parisauli Arsitek Studio and is located in #Jakarta #Indonesia | Photos by @mariowibowo_

node.text:
Dreamy and extravagant Cappadocia mornings via @muratkoksalart, where you can witness the iconic scenery of hot air balloons ebbing and flowing above valleys and "fairy chimneys". 🎈✨

Hot air ballooning is one of the most popular activities in Cappadocia. Though it's available almost all year round, the best time to experience it is from April to November, when weather conditions are more favorable.

Out of all your travels, what's the most surreal destination you've been to? 😍

📽 @muratkoksalart 
📍 Cappadocia, Turkey
🎶 Busta Rhymes - Touch It

node.text:
Waking up to a beautiful day in Tulum with @affyrm.studio and @jenn.elle. Known as one of the most popular destinations on the Mexican Caribbean coast, Tulum is known for its laid-back, close-to-nature lifestyle. 🍃

Besides its pleasant tropical weather, it features white sand beaches, luxurious stays, renowned restaurants, and a calm atmosphere. If you love holistic wellness retreats, you'll surely love it in Tulum. 🇲🇽

How about greeting the day with this grand entrance? Is Tulum your kind of vacation spot? 🌞

📽 @affyrm.studio & @jenn.elle 
📍 #Tulum, #Mexico
🎶 Beyoncé - Love On Top
